result.name: assessment-of-potential-predators-of-plaice-eggs-and-larvae-in-the-irish-sea
result.notes:
Data on fish counts, lengths and stomach contents analysis from fish caught in 
the Irish Sea in 2008 and 2009 to investigate the potential predators of 
plaice eggs. Also included are station data and ichthyoplankton analysis 
counts.
